@page "/freelance"

<PageTitle>Freelance — Devon VanNote</PageTitle>

<div class="section-container">

    <div class="hireme-intro">
        <h1 class="hireme-headline">Fully Managed Websites</h1>
        <p class="hireme-sub">
            I build your site, host it, monitor it, and keep it up to date — you just run your business.
            Fixed pricing, no hourly billing, no surprises.
        </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">What's Included</h2>
    <div class="hireme-why-grid">
        <div class="hireme-why-card">
            <div>
                <h3>Custom Build</h3>
                <p>Your site is built from scratch for your specific needs — no templates, no drag-and-drop editors.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hireme-why-card">
            <div>
                <h3>Hosting Included</h3>
                <p>I handle hosting setup and costs for the first year. Your site is live without you touching a server.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hireme-why-card">
            <div>
                <h3>Uptime Monitoring</h3>
                <p>Your site is monitored around the clock. If something goes down, I know before you do.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hireme-why-card">
            <div>
                <h3>1 Major Change Per Month</h3>
                <p>Small updates under an hour — copy tweaks, photo swaps, price updates — are always included. One major UI change per month is included on top of that.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hireme-why-card">
            <div>
                <h3>Direct Communication</h3>
                <p>You work directly with the developer — not a support ticket queue or an account manager passing notes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hireme-why-card">
            <div>
                <h3>Your Code, If You Leave</h3>
                <p>I manage and maintain the codebase while we work together. If you ever cancel, the full source code is handed over to you.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">Pricing</h2>
    <div class="hireme-packages">

        <div class="hireme-package hireme-package--featured">
            <div class="hireme-package-badge">STATIC SITE</div>
            <div class="hireme-package-tagline" style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
                Brochure sites, portfolios, landing pages — no database required.
            </div>

            <div class="hireme-payment-options">
                <div class="hireme-payment hireme-payment--preferred">
                    <div class="hireme-payment-label">Pay Upfront <span class="hireme-payment-note">Recommended</span></div>
                    <div class="hireme-package-price">$600</div>
                    <p class="hireme-payment-desc">Includes build + full first year of hosting, monitoring &amp; maintenance.</p>
                    <div class="hireme-payment-split">
                        <span>$300 due to start</span>
                        <span class="hireme-payment-split-div">·</span>
                        <span>$300 due at launch</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hireme-payment-divider">— or —</div>
                <div class="hireme-payment">
                    <div class="hireme-payment-label">Spread It Out</div>
                    <div class="hireme-package-price">$62<span>/mo</span></div>
                    <p class="hireme-payment-desc">12 monthly payments — no interest, no fees. Same build and first-year coverage as the upfront option.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hireme-renewal">
                <div class="hireme-renewal-label">>> After Year 1</div>
                <div class="hireme-renewal-options">
                    <div class="hireme-renewal-option">
                        <div class="hireme-renewal-price">$20<span>/mo</span></div>
                        <p>Hosting, uptime monitoring, and one major UI change per month. Small changes under an hour are always included.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hireme-renewal-option-divider">— or —</div>
                    <div class="hireme-renewal-option">
                        <div class="hireme-renewal-price">$15<span>/mo</span></div>
                        <p>Hosting and uptime monitoring only. Small changes under an hour are always included — major UI changes are <strong>$10 each</strong>.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="hireme-package">
            <div class="hireme-package-badge" style="background: var(--lime); color: #000; box-shadow: var(--glow-lime);">DATABASE SITE</div>
            <div class="hireme-package-tagline" style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
                Sites that store, query, or display dynamic data — e-commerce, booking, member portals, etc.
            </div>

            <div class="hireme-payment-options">
                <div class="hireme-payment hireme-payment--preferred">
                    <div class="hireme-payment-label">Flat Fee to Start</div>
                    <div class="hireme-package-price">$1,000</div>
                    <p class="hireme-payment-desc">$1,000 flat fee kicks off the project, then <strong>$125/hr</strong> for the build. Hours are agreed upon before work begins — any hours beyond the estimate are checked with you before proceeding.</p>
                    <div class="hireme-payment-split">
                        <span>$1,000 due to start</span>
                        <span class="hireme-payment-split-div">·</span>
                        <span>Hourly balance due at launch</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hireme-renewal">
                <div class="hireme-renewal-label">>> Monthly Maintenance</div>
                <div class="hireme-renewal-options">
                    <div class="hireme-renewal-option">
                        <div class="hireme-renewal-price">$50–$100<span>/mo</span></div>
                        <p>Hosting, uptime monitoring, database maintenance, and one major UI change per month. Small changes under an hour are always included.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="hireme-stripe-note">
        <span class="hireme-stripe-badge">stripe</span>
        <span>All invoices are sent and payments processed securely through <strong>Stripe</strong>. You'll receive an invoice link via email — no account required to pay.</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
    <div class="hireme-steps">
        <div class="hireme-step">
            <div class="hireme-step-num">01</div>
            <div class="hireme-step-body">
                <h3>Discovery Call / Email</h3>
                <p>Reach out by phone or email to nail down your goals, pages, and features. No commitment required.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hireme-step-connector"></div>
        <div class="hireme-step">
            <div class="hireme-step-num">02</div>
            <div class="hireme-step-body">
                <h3>Build</h3>
                <p>I design and develop your site. You get regular previews and have final say before anything goes live.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hireme-step-connector"></div>
        <div class="hireme-step">
            <div class="hireme-step-num">03</div>
            <div class="hireme-step-body">
                <h3>Launch &amp; Maintain</h3>
                <p>Your site goes live. I handle hosting, monitoring, and up to one major UI change per month throughout the first year. Small changes under an hour are always included.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hireme-step-connector"></div>
        <div class="hireme-step">
            <div class="hireme-step-num">04</div>
            <div class="hireme-step-body">
                <h3>Ongoing Maintenance</h3>
                <p>Continue on a simple monthly subscription — $20/mo for static sites, $50–$100/mo for dynamic sites. Cancel anytime; your code comes with you.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hireme-contact">
        <div class="hireme-contact-inner">
            <h2 class="hireme-contact-heading">Ready to get started?</h2>
            <p class="hireme-contact-sub">Send me a message and I'll get back to you within one business day.</p>
            <a href="mailto:dvannote@outlook.com?subject=Freelance Inquiry" class="hireme-cta hireme-cta--featured hireme-cta--large">
                dvannote&#64;outlook.com
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
